author: violetagg
msg: According to the ServiceLoader specification the name of the provider-configuration file is the fully-qualified binary name of the service's type.
In this case instead of javax.websocket.server.ServerEndpointConfig.Configurator the file name should be javax.websocket.server.ServerEndpointConfig$Configurator.
